OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and cloudy, but also some
OL,7,Fbright spells will occur.
OL,8,FPredominantly dry, but with a chance
OL,9,Fof a little light rain Wednesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures generally average or
OL,11,Fslightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
